Package holiday specialists TravelBird have released the 2016 Inspiring Cities Ranking, putting Nairobi City at number 74 out of the 85 most inspiring cities.Nairobi, however, came 24th in the summer cities ranking. The firm offers a comprehensive ranking of some of the world&#39;s most inspiring destinations or cities. The top 10 inspiring cities from number one are Miami in USA, Bruges in Belgium, San Francisco in USA, Reykjavik in Iceland, Santiago de Compostela in Spain, Salzburg in Austria, Zurich in Switzerland, Heidelberg in Germany and Florence in Italy.The bottom five from 85 are Hanoi in Vietnam, Dakar in Senegal, Mumbai in India, Lima in Peru and Seoul in South Korea.